Privacy Policy:

1. Collection of Information: Our mobile game is designed with a strong commitment to user privacy. We do not gather any personally identifiable information from our users. There is no requirement for users to create accounts or log in to play the game, ensuring a completely anonymous gaming experience.
2. Non-Personal Data: While we do not collect personal information, we may collect non-personal data to enhance the functionality and performance of our game. This data may include information such as device type, operating system, and general gameplay statistics. This information is used solely for internal purposes, such as analyzing trends, identifying areas for improvement, and optimizing the user experience.
3. Data Usage: Any data collected from our users is used exclusively for internal purposes. We do not share this information with any third parties unless required by law or to comply with legal obligations. Our utmost priority is to protect the privacy and confidentiality of our users' data.
4. Use of Cookies: In order to improve user experience, we may use cookies or similar technologies within our mobile game. These technologies serve technical purposes only and do not collect any personal information. Cookies may be used to remember user preferences, track session information, and facilitate smoother gameplay.
5. Consent: By downloading and using our mobile game, users implicitly consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. We prioritize transparency and strive to ensure that our users are fully informed about our data practices.
6. Updates to Privacy Policy: This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our data practices or legal requirements. Any updates or modifications to the policy will be promptly communicated to our users. It is advisable to review this policy regularly to stay informed about our current privacy practices.

If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding our privacy practices, please do not hesitate to contact us at skajgames@gmail.com. We value the privacy of our users and are committed to maintaining the highest standards of data protection.
